{% extends "BASE_README.md.stencil" %}

{% block subtitle %}
Run bash scripts out of your Archerfile.
{% endblock %}

{% block example %}
```json
{
    "name": "SupercoolProject",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "scripts": {
        "greet": {
            "arrow": "{{github}}",
            "command": "echo Hello"
        }
    }
}
```

All parameters will be passed to your script.
```bash
$ archery greet
Hello
$ archery greet World
Hello World
```
{% endblock %}
